## under ``tests/`` whose stem starts with ``test_``. The
## ``repro.nim`` ``build:`` block iterates this list and
## emits one ``pythonUnittest.run(...)`` execute edge per
## entry. Those edges are appended to the same
## ``reprobuildTestExecuteActions`` accumulator as the Nim
## test execute edges, so the ``test`` collection covers
## both languages in one engine pass.
